description: Welcome to 47 Dorchester Street in vibrant South Boston. This spacious and sun-drenched home offers 780 square feet of comfortable living space, featuring 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. The large living area seamlessly opens into an updated kitchen, equipped with stainless steel appliances and elegant countertops, perfect for both everyday living and entertaining, and boasts beautiful wood floors, high ceilings and central air. Enjoy the convenience of heated garage parking in an adjacent building, the private rear deck, ideal for relaxing evenings, or take advantage of the common grassy garden area, complete with outdoor seating and grilling facilities. Additional amenities include bike storage and common laundry facilities. Situated close to a variety of restaurants, shops, and the waterfront with stunning views of the Boston City Skyline. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home your own.
